  "text": "In order to differentiate the ranking function, we employ a method for efficient backpropagation through combinatorial solvers -recently proposed in [CITATION_1] . It turns algorithms or solvers for problems like SHORTEST-PATH, TRAVELING-SALESMAN-PROBLEM, and various graph cuts into differentiable building blocks of neural network architectures.",
